@startuml
title Weather Station System

[*] --> ShutDown

state ShutDown
state ConfigurationMode
state Running
state ControlledMode
state Idle

ShutDown --> Running : Restart / Start
Running --> ConfigurationMode : Changes or Power-Saving Settings Required
ConfigurationMode --> Running : Configuration Completed
Running --> Running : Clock Triggered / Data Collection
Running --> Running : Request for Weather Summary / Prepare and Send
Running --> Running : Request for Status / Check and Transmit
Running --> ControlledMode : Remote Control / Move to Controlled Mode
Running --> ShutDown : Shutdown Command / Shut Down
ConfigurationMode --> Running : Configuration Completed
ControlledMode --> Running : Return to Running State

Idle --> Running : Restart / Start

@enduml
